  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Summary of Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Able to voluntarily provide written informed consent to participate in the study.

          -  User Performance Accuracy Testing Only: Self-Monitoring - Subject is currently
             performing unassisted self-monitoring of blood glucose.

          -  For subjects participating in the In Vivo Glucose adjustment procedure age range is 18
             - 45.

        Summary of Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Female subjects who are pregnant or lactating.

          -  Subjects who, in the opinion of the Investigator, are unsuitable for participation in
             the study.

          -  User Performance Accuracy Testing Only -Prior involvement with the investigational
             BGMS being used in this study.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
